creator: James Elroy Flecker
description:
LibriVox recording of Forty-Two Poems by James Elroy Flecker.
Read in English by Ian King; Peter Tucker; Steve C; Rosslyn Carlyle; Marina Tsung; Shakira Searle; Eric Metzler; Claudia Salto; Greg Giordano; Jordan Heron; Diana Majlinger; Joseph Schnebelen; Anusha Iyer; DomBombadil; Jill Clancy; Paul Cecchetti; Andrei Borissenko; Martin Geeson; Rob Baker; Chris Pyle
This is a collection of poems by James Elroy Flecker. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
